		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Authoritative scripture of Hinduism, created by Rishis (sages), after inspired creativity</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For microtones in Indian music, see <a href="/wiki/Shruti_(music)" title="Shruti (music)">Shruti (music)</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Shruti_(disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect mw-disambig" title="Shruti (disambiguation)">Shruti (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
